# It is important to have AI guide us.
Ask prompts such as:
* What do you think about XYZ idea?
* How can I improve my idea?
* Is my idea worth pursuing?

These prompts force the AI to think and argue against us or with us.
The reason we want the AI to disagree is that 9/10 ideas have already
been done. We want the AI to research this and tell us. We do not want
the idea to blindly follow everything we say like a sheep.
